Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,[Speaking Croatian] {I could possibly ask someone to tl this if needed - juggen}

Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:34.28,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the third round of the women's 52 kg competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:37.65,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's Yokomizo is down a Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:39.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get around her! Get around her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:40.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep moving your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:44.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Italy's Mastroianni with a Kosoto Gari!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:45.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ippon! Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.35,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokomizo is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:56.81,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's women's team has yet to win a gold medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:02:04.11,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,So now we place our last hopes on Inokuma Yawara, who will compete in the 48kg-and-unders tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:09.85,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, who will represent us in the open-weight matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:16.86,epTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.3\be1\pos(320,340)\3c&H3548D5&\c&H4E30E2&}First Time Under Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:27.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}So you're the final hope to win a gold medal tomorrow, Inokuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Care to share your enthusiasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:31.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Enthusiasm? Now wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm about to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about carefree! Going shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're BBC UK!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:42.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to see your Ippon Zeoi tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:44.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be entering the open-weight competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Inokuma-san is even grabbing international headlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:50.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jody!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving! Fujiko, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, just ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:07.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the 7-dan, 8-dan, no, 9-dan black belt will answer any question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:14.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're Yawara Inokuma's grandfather, Master Jigoro? We're BBC UK.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:17.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,BCG? What are you, a vaccine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara, let's go look at that souvenir shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:27.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Jody-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Fujiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:36.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san has her match tomorrow. Are you sure we should be doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:40.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am. Yawara's feeling pressure for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:44.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's feeling discouraged, not to mention tense, without Matsuda around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:47.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Will she be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:49.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're taking her out on the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She needs to have a little fun, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:55.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:55.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:10.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You're actually going to give that hat to Hanazono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He might look really cute in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:16.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Found one! I'm getting this poncho for my darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:17.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you chosen something, Yawara?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:20.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A souvenir for Matsuda, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. You need to get him something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:29.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He already goes lots of places to cover events. He doesn't need a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? It'll make him happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about these shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:35.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides... Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:42.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kosaku gets excited and bored with things really easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:46.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once someone becomes a superstar, he gets bored with them right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:55.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I almost forgot, Yawara!\N We're going to have some cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:58.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right! Let's sweeten things up with some cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make it a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:02.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:09.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My five, six, no, seven national titles could not have been accomplished in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First — practice. Second — practice. And skipping third and fourth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff yourself with good food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:22.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Master Jigoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:25.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that everything in life is connected to judo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:29.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quick to catch on, BCG.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:32.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As we say, "You don't make war on an empty stomach."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.44,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.16,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He somehow turned the interview into one of his lectures.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.25,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He's enchanted not just the reporters</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:41.36,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,but also the foreign athletes who don't understand a word.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.11,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, Master Inokuma Jigoro!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:48.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Coach, we need to enter someone for tomorrow's open-weight matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh right, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:58.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohdoh, will your leg be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:00.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Coach! It's coming along fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:08.13,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Tohdoh can't manage the open-weights with that pain.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:14.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Takabe was in peak form for the 72kg-and-under matches,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but now she has this hip thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:18.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. How about Obayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:22.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw how she lost to that Canadian, Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:25.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still pretty devastated about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess it'll have to be Inokuma Yawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's go with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The 48kg-and-under and open-weight classes are held consecutively,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I know she can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:45.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:50.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Coach. Boy, oh boy, that interview turned into a full autograph session.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:55.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you did honor them with a very profound discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Coach, have you decided who'll compete in the open-weight matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:06.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm about to enter her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know it might be too much to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've been agonizing over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:13.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:16.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:26.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Japanese female judo players have caught my fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:28.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've written their names on my palms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:33.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So which will be your entrant, left or right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:39.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Which? Master, are you sure this is the best way to decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:43.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how! Both of them are pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.96,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These are players that live up to the standards</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:53.61,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,of internationally renowned judoka, Master Jigoro.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.38,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,One must be Inokuma Yawara.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:08:02.08,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other... actually rivals Inokuma Yawara?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.96,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,If he says it, then there's no mistake about it.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, wait! This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:20.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This one? Remember, a judoka always sticks to his word!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko, you really bought a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:47.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm not competing, I'm focusing all my strength on shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:53.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you give it a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:01.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san has a very important match tomorrow, so please let her be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Inokuma-san is one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:07.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...but right now we want to interview you! That's right, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You never cease to amaze us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were suddenly picked as a regular competitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:17.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell us how you feel about being a Cinderella?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:18.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A regular competitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:21.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:24.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about how Ito Fujiko-san got picked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To compete in tomorrow's open-weight matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:47.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Beanpole, eat up! No need to watch your weight for the open-weights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to eat now while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:54.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow you'll be too nervous to have an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:54.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already lost my appetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:05.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't wait for tomorrow's matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:08.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see your big exploits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You look down, Yawara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Fujiko-san's nervousness rubbing off on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:19.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting nervous over this little tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:23.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a warm-up for the Barcelona Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:28.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, what did you write on the palms of your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:29.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just some written charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:36.61,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Left hand: Fujiko\NRight hand: Ito#
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:41.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Yawara has to compete in the open-weights!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:45.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the reason why I entered the open-weights!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Teleshikova.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:51.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave Inokuma Yawara to Khrushchev.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't slack off just because Yawara isn't in the open-weights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:11:01.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Jigoro, who trained Yawara, also coached the player who's replacing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara is my only opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:06.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:20.96,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. All this flying, and I'm still not there!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:26.34,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll win the 48kg-and-unders, right, Yawara-san?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:31.16,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And are you entering the open-weights?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.85,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara-san.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:43.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether she's the world champion or the strongest woman around,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,she's still a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:50.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't hurt to try for her, at least while you're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:31.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Inokuma-san. Did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:34.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't sleep either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:37.99,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Inokuma-san is nervous?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:41.15,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So she really does feel disheartened without Matsuda-san.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.29,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame you, Fujiko-san.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:47.12,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They picked you to compete the day before the tournament.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:56.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry! You'll come back to Japan wearing the gold medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:13:00.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten really good yourself, Fujiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:01.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:05.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going back to Japan after losing in the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really do want to go back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That way you can see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:15.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, that way we can eat ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:19.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I want to eat ramen! And maybe some soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:24.93,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I better not get her worked up by mentioning Matsuda-san.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I have something for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:28.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:29.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dried plums!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:34.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, take one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:46.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:46.78,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:49.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.31,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me want to cry.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.25,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to hold back.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:01.48,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san must be feeling lonely too.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.77,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell her I'm scared.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:07.49,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only make Fujiko-san more nervous.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:14.03,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, why? Why am I so scared?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:28.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, now that I've had my fill of breakfast, it's time to move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:31.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Laugh or cry, this is our last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We must do our very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be crying? Come on, laugh it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be a whole lot of laughing once we get our gold medals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They've just announced the pairings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:46.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because nobody in the 48 kg class is competing in the open-weight class,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:50.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,both sets of matches will be held at the same time in Rings A and B.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So what about the pairings?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:58.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yawara won't have any problems against France's Deneuve in the opening round.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:00.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the open-weights, Ito will be facing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:04.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Martinez of Cuba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:09.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She gave Canada's Rockwell a run for her money in the 72 kg heavyweight title match!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:14.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Listen, don't tell Ito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a nervous wreck as it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:19.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If she finds out who she's fighting first, she'll faint!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:24.10,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So Beanpole will be facing that Manekineko first?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:37.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I forgot my belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:39.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you forgot your belt? Someone lend her theirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a white belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:43.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:47.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no white belts in the World Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:49.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone give her a black belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:50.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:51.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have put her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should start warming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamatsuri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:20.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:24.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I know full well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's normal for someone to get scared before a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:27.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:34.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? This isn't like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Remember how you usually handle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:41.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You won the World Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:46.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:49.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That loudmouth Matsuda-san isn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:53.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can enjoy ourselves much more here than at Seoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:57.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, that Matsuda-san was always hovering around you like a moth—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.54,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:07.81,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is Matsuda-san's absence making Yawara-san so...</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.37,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:22.20,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's just too absurd.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:27.44,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. There's no way I'd lose out to that third-rate perpetual hack.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:30.44,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no possible way.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be all right, Yawara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:37.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I'm right here to look after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:38.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:43.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Superstar Yawara-chan spends quality time with her boyfriend before the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a big scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't just sneak a picture of us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:51.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything a superstar does is newsworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:54.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Kosaku would say this is a nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:58.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara-san, don't worry. I'll just recover the film...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:17:58.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:20.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've finally made it to Belgrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:25.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have arrived later than usual, but I'll make it to the first round!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:32.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pioneer Hall! You know, yes? Pioneer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:36.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Pioneer! Of Belgrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:39.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Belgrade? No, no! Zagreb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zagray... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:51.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you speak English. English! But keep it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fog! Belgrade, fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:55.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn to Zagreb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:57.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:04.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zagreb is Yugoslavia's second largest city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:07.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And that guy just said "fog."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:10.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:12.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't able to land in Belgrade because of fog?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:16.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so they went to Zagreb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:25.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So how does that black belt feel on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:29.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up straight, dang it!\N We can't even see that black belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:34.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! It's time to put some finishing touches on your "un, deux, trois"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:38.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, but Inokuma-san's about to begin her first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:42.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about Yawara. Worry about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:44.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hone your "un, deux, trois"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.79,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.07,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. I'm scared.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:07.80,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why am I so scared?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:11.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:13.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck! Win this for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:17.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry! Inokuma-san will come through for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:20.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my fated rival, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:25.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohdoh, since when did you become her "fated rival"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:28.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I'll be rooting for you, just for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:29.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma, you're up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, go get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight hard! We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:42.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Just take me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:44.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Belgrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Belgrade, Pioneer Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:56.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how far is it to Belgrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:57.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Driver, show me the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:00.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The map! Map!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:04.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so we're in Zagreb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:07.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Belgrade... Belgrade...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:10.70,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Four hundred twenty kilometers?!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:14.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait a minute! Driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.63,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma Yawara finally makes her appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.76,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in Japan has been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.36,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the world has been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:29.09,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma Yawara has appeared in the 48kg-and-unders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.09,0:21:32.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamashita-san, Inokuma is finally competing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's been a long wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:40.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Ippon Zeoi in the All-Japan Championships was as polished as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:45.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her first international tournament since the World Cup, but she'll pull it off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:49.69,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma's first opponent is the freshman player from France, Deneuve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:52.76,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Just based on their records, is this Inokuma's game to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:00.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san, fight her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:03.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara-san, it's all right! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:11.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, quit rubbernecking and do your "un, deux, trois"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:13.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:27.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:38.96,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Deneuve with an Uchi Mata!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:40.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:54.85,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: The Barcelona Olympics in {\c&H5C74FF&}271{\r} Days#
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:22:59.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara, what in blue blazes was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:01.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is where you're gonna lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:04.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,then you're doing a hundred belly crawls on the Trans-Siberian Railway!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:07.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Fujiko-san's match has already started!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:09.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that idiot up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.61,0:23:13.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san, hang in there! Un, deux, trois!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:16.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You dang-blasted losers! I'm through with all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:16.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:19.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Swan Lake on the World's Stage.
